				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/Ai-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-qu%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-ZTWsVOUR627dBLASBKN9Xg">Ai Phạm quân kỳ 3 - 哀范君其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-TXAaCmjdRWIV6MkCYE1psQ">Lỗ Tấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/H%E1%BA%A1-v%C5%A9/poem-1WwuWOOTnqta5CuA9yU9AQ">Hạ vũ - 賀雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-S%C4%A9-Thuy%C3%AAn/Khai-Ti%C3%AAn-b%E1%BB%99c-b%E1%BB%91/poem-V8NLrnKAop8pgey0uChMFQ">Khai Tiên bộc bố - 開先瀑布</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-S%C4%A9-Thuy%C3%AAn/author-W2mWmkTR4UigR3MuaZOlSg">Tưởng Sĩ Thuyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1t/S%C6%A1n-%C4%91%C3%A0m-thu-di%E1%BB%83u/poem-JellBKxcAqaL7-LLA2YuDg">Sơn đàm thu diểu - 山潭秋眺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1t/author-QedIvlr4BuYMTZh_TuTCTA">Nguyễn Đức Đạt</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Ph%C3%B9ng/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-An-d%E1%BA%A1-v%C5%A9/poem-mQIW0xgRIvVVF29oWDFU6Q">Trường An dạ vũ - 長安夜雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Ph%C3%B9ng/author-2lovo1tul_9ix8CytGMv0Q">Tiết Phùng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1-Thi%C3%AAn-b%E1%BA%A1n-qu%E1%BA%A7n-s%C6%A1n-c%C3%B4-th%E1%BA%A3o-%C4%91%C3%ACnh/poem-hLEaiatt1BgJcDpIRCjbYg">Tức sự (Thiên bạn quần sơn cô thảo đình) - 即事（天畔群山孤草亭）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%9Ac-V%C4%83n/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C6%B0-th%E1%BB%A5-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-U_1Ea5w3Tq93blzoXUzU0Q">Tương tư thụ kỳ 3 - 相思樹其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%9Ac-V%C4%83n/author-xVo9muuF2eAhEr09snbNTQ">Úc Văn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/V%C4%A9nh-Giang-nguy%E1%BB%87t-phi%E1%BA%BFm/poem-NgP8Ps3jLEkIfKodUAvqXA">Vĩnh Giang nguyệt phiếm - 永江月泛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/author-n8TXz8ZnEQ2g7U6IvK74Vw">Nguyễn Trung Ngạn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-K%E1%BB%B3/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-XV/poem-OmGFvpb1-fdvi4DgXVaDZw">Vô đề (XV) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-K%E1%BB%B3/author-1swHDuDfqhjQRVvirtpDBQ">Phạm Kỳ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Dung/Xu%C3%A2n-du-h%E1%BB%93i-v%C4%83n-thi/poem-YFIj-vYYJTb3lrmUtTaN_g">Xuân du hồi văn thi - 春遊回文詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Dung/author-qXPPibIiYGXM8D15wPwoFg">Vương Dung</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
